Acknowledgments
----------------
FreeAgent was inspired by the open-source AI coding agent community.
The features common to these tools — local model serving, tool execution,
permission models, streaming chat, MCP/LSP integration — reflect widely shared
patterns in the ecosystem rather than any single project's unique contribution.
FreeAgent is an independent implementation that contributes its own kernel,
architecture, and tooling back to that community.

Third-party libraries remain under their respective licenses.
